    <body>
        <section name="scalamojo-maven-plugin">
            <p>The scalamojo-maven-plugin is an extension of the maven-plugin-plugin plugin report to decorate mojo
                descriptors extracted by the
                <a href="http://maven.apache.org/plugin-tools/maven-plugin-tools-annotations/index.html">Maven Plugin Tool for Annotations</a>
                with additional mojo and parameter details extracted from scaladoc: description, @since, @deprecated.</p>
            <p>If there are problems please let me know.</p>
        </section>
        <section name="Requirements">
            <ul>
                <li>Maven 3.0</li>
                <li>JDK 1.5</li>
                <li><bold>No need to install <a href="http://scala-lang.org">scala</a> !</bold></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
       <p>Thanks to David Bernard and the team responsible for the <a href="http://davidb.github.com/scala-maven-plugin/">scala-maven-plugin</a>, which I use to compile all my maven plugins and whose generated maven site structure I lifted completely for my own use.</p>
    </body>
